  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 200°C (400°F).",
    "Roast the chestnuts in the oven for 15 minutes, or until tender.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the diced red bell pepper and cook for 3 minutes, or until tender.",
    "Add the smoked chicken breast and cook for 2 minutes, or until heated through.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the mixed greens, roasted chestnuts, and smoked chicken breast mixture.",
    "Top with crumbled goat cheese and a drizzle of balsamic vinaigrette.",
    "Sprinkle with diced fresh parsley, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
